main event: A UFO sighting was reported in Medford, Mass. on April 9, 1952, describing an initial white colored cigar-shaped object.
interesting points: The object was reported to have a high speed and performed unusual maneuvers,The observer was the only confirmed witness to the sighting,The conclusion drawn was that there was insufficient data for evaluation,The sighting left the observer with a highly doubtful impression,Comments included some unclear terms like 'sensor lint'.
